description:
Package with the "net", "crypto" and "url" libraries of the Chromium codebase as a C++ static library.
        Packed libraries: net.lib, crcrypto.lib, url_lib.lib, http_server.lib, sdch.lib and dependencies.
        MSBuild will add the package's headers to compiler include directories and the necessary libraries to the linker, if applicable.
title: Chromium net static library
